The post caption mentions reminiscing about a performance with @daftpunk_discovery and thanks @jeff_s_sheppard for capturing the moment.

The image is a promotional post for Jesslyn's new single called "Strawberries". It features an orange background with the title of the song and the artist's name in yellow text, along with a shadow of a person's hands. The caption indicates the song is about to be released and encourages pre-saving.

The image shows Jesslyn_music in a sparkly, floor-length gown. The caption mentions "Smart casual" and tags @alamourthelabel, suggesting she's wearing a dress from that brand.
The image shows Jesslyn in a black dress with a train, posing in what appears to be a luxurious hallway. The post is captioned "Va Va Voom" and credits @khirzadfemme.

The image shows a person in a home studio setting, likely engaged in songwriting. There's a keyboard, microphone, headphones, and a notebook with lyrics visible. The caption also mentions "songwriting sessions + soul food".
